    INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [c.Color2] ON [c2].[ColorId] = [c.Color2].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [c.Product2] ON [c2].[ProductId] = [c.Product2].[Id]

    INNER JOIN [Bills] AS [c.Bill2] ON [c2].[BillId] = [c.Bill2].[Id]

) AS [t2] ON [c.Product.ProductCategory.Products].[CategoryId] = [t2].[Id0]
